data.title: Dirt fill
data.description: Free fill. Dirt from a yard good for filling in areas. Machine on site to load trucks. Job will be stating week after labor. Delivery in 6 wheel dump (3/5 ) yards per load may be available for local delivery for a fee. 50-80 yards available.

data.title: Free fill take as much as you want
data.description: Have about 150-200 yards of dirt/sand fill. Rocks and stones are staying. You must load and truck it out yourself. If you see this ad up I will still have some. If interested please leave name and number.

data.title: Free Loam / Dirt
data.description: Free loam / dirt leftover from a walkway project. Mostly loam but has some crushed stone mixed in. Great to fill in any low spot in a yard. The pile has easy access, right in the front driveway next to the street. Bring a shovel and a truck and help  ...
